这里很安全  佐伊  我不是他
This is safe, Zoe. I'm not him.

95
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:15,370
早上好  杰姬
Good morning, Jackie.

96
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,660
早上好
Good morning.

97
